            <title>[SOLR-10439] SchemaField.getNamedPropertyValues doesn&apos;t include &apos;large&apos;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-10439</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I just noticed SchemaField.getNamedPropertyValues refers to most/all of FieldProperties constants. This is a maintenance problem; it&apos;d be nice if there were a test to ensure properties don&apos;t get forgotten.  &lt;tt&gt;LARGE&lt;/tt&gt; was forgotten.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
